The [Vassar Feetech Servo SDK](https://github.com/vassar-robotics/feetech-servo-sdk) provides a Python implementation of [`set_middle_position`](https://github.com/vassar-robotics/feetech-servo-sdk/blob/d60242c8e1d17ffc97ea5723e1256a5def86414f/vassar_feetech_servo_sdk/controller.py#L453)
